---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageSchema = { '@context': 'https://schema.org', '@type': 'MedicalWebPage', name: 'Crisis Resources: Regain Hope Detox and Recovery Center', reviewedBy: { '@type': 'Person', name: 'Mileidys Gomez Gonzalez, MD' } };
---
<Layout
  title="Crisis Resources & Emergency Help | Regain Hope Detox and Recovery Center"
  description="In crisis? Call 988 (Suicide & Crisis Lifeline) or 911 now. Free, confidential help is available 24/7. Crisis and overdose resources for you or a loved one."
  schema={pageSchema}
>
  <section class="minihero"><div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">You are not alone</span>
    <h1>Crisis Resources: Help Is Available Right Now</h1>
    <p>If you're in crisis, you don't have to wait or figure this out alone. These free, confidential resources are available 24/7.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section><div class="container rich" style="max-width:820px;">
    <div class="callout">
      <b>If you or someone else is in immediate danger, call 911 now.</b><br />
      Suicide &amp; Crisis Lifeline: <b>call or text 988</b>, free, confidential, 24/7.
    </div>

    <h2>Immediate help, 24/7</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><b>988 Suicide &amp; Crisis Lifeline</b>: call or text <b>988</b>, or chat at 988lifeline.org. Free, confidential, 24/7. (Press 1 for the Veterans Crisis Line; marca 2 para español.)</li>
      <li><b>911</b>: for any medical emergency or immediate danger.</li>
      <li><b>Crisis Text Line</b>: text <b>HOME</b> to <b>741741</b>.</li>
      <li><b>SAMHSA National Helpline</b>: <b>1-800-662-HELP (4357)</b>, free, confidential, 24/7 treatment referral and information (English &amp; Spanish).</li>
      <li><b>Veterans Crisis Line</b>: dial <b>988 then press 1</b>, or text <b>838255</b>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>If you think someone is overdosing</h2>
    <p><b>Call 911 immediately.</b> If you have <b>naloxone (Narcan)</b>, administer it. It can reverse an opioid overdose and is safe to use even if you're not sure opioids are involved. Stay with the person until help arrives. Many California pharmacies and the state's Naloxone Distribution Project provide naloxone; ask us how to get it.</p>

    <h2>More resources</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><b>SAMHSA treatment locator</b>: findtreatment.gov</li>
      <li><b>NAMI HelpLine</b> (mental health support): 1-800-950-NAMI (6264)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>When you're ready for treatment, we're here</h2>
    <p>A crisis line can keep you safe today; treatment helps build a safer tomorrow. When you're ready, Regain Hope Detox and Recovery Center offers physician-led medical detox and residential care in Burbank, and our admissions line is open 24/7 at <a href="tel:+18182644388">(818) 264-4388</a>. There's no pressure; reach out whenever you're ready. You can also <a href="/admissions/verify-insurance/">verify your insurance</a> or <a href="/programs/medical-detox/">learn about our programs</a>.</p>
  </div></section>
</Layout>
